<p><strong>本市户籍儿童所需材料</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201125/398ce8d3e4c84bc8b03213931964f165.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>非本市户籍儿童所需材料</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201125/dec6831633254bfa8ec2b8a66e71eeb2.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
